text: Harshita Shekhar Gaur (born 12 October 1992) is an Indian actress known for her work on the youth-based show Sadda Haq, in which she played the lead role of Sanyukta Agarwal and Dimpy Pandit in the 2018 web series Mirzapur. == References == ==Other websites== * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Indian movie actors Category:Indian television actors Category:Indian soap opera actors Category:Indian television presenters Category:Actors in Hindi television
